query:
SELECT g.id, g.nome, COUNT(re.id) as total_exames
FROM gestantes g
LEFT JOIN resultadosExames re ON g.id = re.gestanteId
WHERE g.nome LIKE '%Débora%'
GROUP BY g.id, g.nome;
